"title": "2570: Jesus Christ, suffering of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2570",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ's life was characterised by suffering, though the worst experiences were reserved for his final days. His sufferings are both redemptive and an example to believers.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's sufferings foretold</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:6-Ps22:8\">PSA 22:6–22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:16-Ps22:18\">PSA 22:16–22:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:6\">ISA 50:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:13-Isa53:12\">ISA 52:13–53:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9-Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:9–9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:7\">ZEC 13:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:11\">1PE 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>In Jesus Christ's predictions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:17-Matt20:19\">MAT 20:17–20:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:32-Mark10:34\">MRK 10:32–10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31-Luke18:32\">LUK 18:31–18:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:32-John12:33\">JHN 12:32–12:33</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's suffering during his lifetime</h2>\n<h3>As a child</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13-Matt2:15\">MAT 2:13–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Because of his family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:20-Mark3:21\">MRK 3:20–3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:3-John7:5\">JHN 7:3–7:5</a></p>\n<h3>Because of the crowds' unbelief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:19\">MRK 9:19</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:17\">MAT 17:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:41\">LUK 9:41</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:39\">MAT 12:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:29\">LUK 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:11-Mark8:12\">MRK 8:11–8:12</a></p>\n<h3>Because of the disciples' slowness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:17-Mark8:21\">MRK 8:17–8:21</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8-Matt16:11\">MAT 16:8–16:11</a></p>\n<h3>Because of the religious leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:14\">MAT 12:14</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:6\">MRK 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:11\">LUK 6:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:18\">JHN 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:1\">JHN 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:48\">JHN 8:48</a></p>\n<h3>Because of human suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:41\">LUK 19:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:34\">MRK 7:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:13\">LUK 7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:33-John11:35\">JHN 11:33–11:35</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's suffering at the time of his death</h2>\n<h3>He was inwardly troubled</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:36-Matt26:42\">MAT 26:36–26:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:32-Mark14:39\">MRK 14:32–14:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:40-Luke22:44\">LUK 22:40–22:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21\">JHN 13:21</a></p>\n<h3>He was betrayed</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:21-Matt26:25\">MAT 26:21–26:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:17-Mark14:21\">MRK 14:17–14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:21-Luke22:23\">LUK 22:21–22:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:47-Matt26:49\">MAT 26:47–26:49</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:43-Mark14:45\">MRK 14:43–14:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:47-Luke22:48\">LUK 22:47–22:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:2-John18:5\">JHN 18:2–18:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:18-John13:30\">JHN 13:18–13:30</a></p>\n<h3>He was humiliated</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:27-Matt27:30\">MAT 27:27–27:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:16-Mark15:19\">MRK 15:16–15:19</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:67-Matt26:68\">MAT 26:67–26:68</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:65\">MRK 14:65</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:63-Luke22:65\">LUK 22:63–22:65</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:26\">MAT 27:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:15\">MRK 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:22\">LUK 23:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:11\">LUK 23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:22\">JHN 18:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:1\">JHN 19:1</a></p>\n<h3>He was crucified</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:33\">LUK 23:33</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:35\">MAT 27:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:25\">MRK 15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:18\">JHN 19:18</a></p>\n<h3>He suffered separation from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:46\">LUK 23:46</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's attitude to his suffering</h2>\n<h3>He did not retaliate in his suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:12-Matt27:14\">MAT 27:12–27:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:3-Mark15:5\">MRK 15:3–15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a></p>\n<h3>He grew through the experience of suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8\">HEB 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:10\">HEB 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's sufferings were necessary for salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:26-Luke24:27\">LUK 24:26–24:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46-Luke24:47\">LUK 24:46–24:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:3\">ACT 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:23\">ACT 26:23</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ suffered as a unique sacrifice</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:27\">HEB 7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:25-Heb9:26\">HEB 9:25–9:26</a></p>\n<h2>The Christian experience of suffering</h2>\n<h3>Believers share in Jesus Christ's sufferings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:5\">2CO 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:34–25:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:4-Acts9:5\">ACT 9:4–9:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:7-Acts22:8\">ACT 22:7–22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:15\">ACT 26:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's sufferings are an example for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:18-John16:20\">JHN 16:18–16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5-Phil2:7\">PHP 2:5–2:7</a></p>",
